headline: Navan Names Aurélien Nolf as Chief Financial Officer
summary: PALO ALTO, Calif., February 11, 2026--Navan (NASDAQ: NAVN), the global AI-powered business travel and expense platform, today announced the appointment of Aurélien Nolf as Chief Financial Officer, effective March 2, 2026.
